  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t现在普遍预测国内一二线城市房价还会缓慢上涨一段时间，再往后大概持平或微涨，而三四线城市以及再往下的小地方房价已经到了天花板了，<br/>\n<br/>\n就业形势也是，三四线城市已经基本成功实现单休常态化，工资3，4000常态化了。高级人才都去了一二线强市，剩下的普通人拿着微薄的收入在本地做着并不轻松的工作。<br/>\n<br/>\n三四线城市将来会被国家放弃吗？发展是否已经完全到头了？已经成为了一二线强市的人肉电池供应商？<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS96TUpaRHJOLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/zMJZDrN.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/zMJZDrN.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zMJZDrN.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS8xQ05EOXpzLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/1CND9zs.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1CND9zs.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1CND9zs.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9HenNNeGxzLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/GzsMxls.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/GzsMxls.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GzsMxls.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9VWFA0R2plLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/UXP4Gje.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/UXP4Gje.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UXP4Gje.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
